title: Left 4 Dead Lives (Kinda) - Kinda Funny Games Daily 03.14.19
description:
Start your trial month of Hims for $5 at http://forhims.com/gamesdaily

O'Neal Johnson -- https://www.twitch.tv/dad0fwar -- joins Greg to talk about Turtle Rock's new co-op zombie game!

Time Stamps - 
http://loveforachild.org
O’Neal J. Johnson - twitch.tv/dad0fwar
00:07:48 - Housekeeping
The Roper Report   -
00:09:09 - WBIE and Turtle Rock Announce “Back 4 Blood”
00:16:21 - “Turns out the way to get a 3 out of Valve is to leave and change the name.” - Malcontent Ronin
00:20:43 - Let’s Walk Back the Sony/Take Two Rumors
00:23:56 - Fortnite Changes Switch/Mobile Crossplay
00:29:09 - BAFTA Game Awards Nominations 2019
00:36:50 - Out today
00:37:59 - “Beat Saber's DLC is out now and IT’S GREAT.” - Dapper Stephen
00:39:57 - “Why does it seem EA likes to release things to basically get cannibalized by its own games?” - Alex Russ
00:44:06 -  Hims
Reader mail   -
00:45:14 - “What do you think the big Fall 2019 PlayStation game will be?” - Addison Thyng
00:52:00 - “A report is out stating that Ninja was allegedly paid one million dollars by EA to play Apex on launch day.” - Alex Russ
00:57:25 - Squad Up: Gary - PS4 - You_Stay_Classy_ - The Division/The Division 2
00:58:45 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s host: Greg & Steve Saylor
